    "entity.transliteratedOtherNames[]) read directly. Each query string is either",
    "  - a verbatim copy of one of those name fields (category != typo), or",
    "  - a documented single-word/char mutation of such a field (category == typo),",
    "  - a documented 'core' shortening of the legalName field (category *_core).",
    "So the LEI<->name mapping is GLEIF's own assertion, not our guess. Whether an",
    "endpoint surfaces that LEI for that string is exactly what the harness measures.",
    "Harvested 2026-07-16 via api.gleif.org (see git commit for the harvest run)."
